/* inventory movements data and purcharses data
	I used pgadmin CSV import method to import the data from CSV
	
	How to do it?
	- Go to bd_jorge_carmona_mulata > shcemas > public > tables
	- Right click to the desired table (e.g. riwi_purcharses)
	- Click on import/export data-
	- Select Import
	- in Filename Paste or search the filepath and it's name
	- in Format select csv
	- in encoding select UTF8
	- Go to options tab
	- Activate Header check
	- Click OK
